</LG>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>Stedfastlych<NOTE PLACE="foot">Stedfastlyche O, stedefastly D.</NOTE> &thorn;ey preyd a-none<NOTE PLACE="foot">al oon D.</NOTE></L>
