<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>By<NOTE PLACE="foot">Be OD.</NOTE> &thorn;ys ensample may &yogh;e see</L>
<L>&THORN;at god ys euer ful of pyte;</L>
<L>&THORN;ogh<NOTE PLACE="foot">&yogh;if D.</NOTE> a man hym onys forsake,</L>
