<L N="365">&yogh;yf &thorn;an &thorn;y erende<NOTE PLACE="foot">&yogh;if &thorn;ou &thorn;in arende not D.</NOTE> spede ne sette,</L>
<L>&thorn;an<NOTE PLACE="foot">&THORN;anne O.</NOTE> wylt &thorn;ou curse hym<NOTE PLACE="foot">hem O, banne hym D.</NOTE> &thorn;at &thorn;ou mette.</L>
<L>Hyt ys &thorn;e tycement<NOTE PLACE="foot">&thorn;is is &thorn;e tysyng D.</NOTE> of &thorn;e deuyl</L>
