</LG>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>&YOGH;yf &thorn;ey come nat<NOTE PLACE="foot">noghte O.</NOTE> also &thorn;urgh<NOTE PLACE="foot">comyn only of D.</NOTE> &thorn;oght,</L>
