<L N="444">&thorn;at tokene ys<NOTE PLACE="foot">takyn it D.</NOTE> of selkou&thorn;e &thorn;yng,<NOTE PLACE="foot">selkow&thorn; &thorn;ynge O.</NOTE></L>
